column5: I bought 23 spark plugs off ebay and in the pack, 3 were not the same as what I ordered.  Since I got a good deal on the lot, I am not going to complain to the seller.  Since I have no use for them, I'll give them to anyone who wants them.  The ones I am giving away are NGK's BUHW-2.  If anyone is in the Woodbridge area, PM me and I will arrange a time for you to pick them up.
